  "short_description": "WHAT THE PAK?! is a minigame-rush party game with fast-paced gameplay for up to 8 players. Our various mini-games are designed so you can pull off all kinds of shenanigans with your friends. Punch them, lick them… Steal their chickens before throwing them overboard.",
